* 2000 - Wild and Wicked 
* 2001 - The Complete Limelight Sessions
* 2004 - Greatest Hits
* 2005 - Beginnings

=== 混音專輯 ===

* 1999 - Come On Over: International Version
* 2002 - Up! (country mix 和 pop remix 雙專輯)

